'''莫克镇战役'''是叙利亚内战期间发生于[[哈马省|哈马省]]的一场战役，交战双方是反对派武装和叙利亚政府军。这场战役是围绕着莫克镇（Mork）进行的。2014年2月1日，该镇被反对派武装占领，之后政府军一直试图夺回该镇。

==反对派占领莫克镇==

2月1日，据报道反对派武装占领了莫克镇北部的al-Harsh检查站和位于Helfaya与Taybat al-Imam之间的al-Jeser检查站。反对派还占领了al-Aboud检查站，之后完全控制了莫克镇并切断了通往Wadi al-Daif与[[迈阿赖努阿曼|迈阿赖努阿曼]]附近al-Hamidiyah军事基地的补给线，并孤立了位于Khan Shaykhun的政府军检查站。通过这一系列军事行动，反对派武装成功与[[哈马_(叙利亚)|哈马]]市东部与西部郊区之间的反对派取得汇合。<ref name="mork1">{{Cite web |url=http://syriahr.com/en/index.php?option=com_news&nid=1467&Itemid=2&task=displaynews#.UzokHvmSykE |title=Advances for rebel and Islamic fighters in Hama |accessdate=2014-04-20 |archive-date=2014-02-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140223174816/http://syriahr.com/en/index.php?option=com_news&nid=1467&Itemid=2&task=displaynews#.UzokHvmSykE |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="mork2">[http://www.aranews.org/en/home/syria/997-syria-rebels-control-strategic-area-near-hama.html Syria rebels control strategic area near Hama] {{webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20140401122800/http://www.aranews.org/en/home/syria/997-syria-rebels-control-strategic-area-near-hama.html |date=2014-04-01 }}</ref>

==政府军的反攻==

2月3日，在Soran大桥附近，反对派武装与一支正驶往莫克镇的政府军车队交火。根据叙利亚人权观察组织（SOHR）的报道，在战斗中至少有20名政府军丧生。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://syriahr.com/en/index.php?option=com_news&nid=1494&Itemid=2&task=displaynews#.Uzor__mSykE |title=violent clashes and losses in regime side in Hama |accessdate=2014-04-20 |archive-date=2014-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407100555/http://syriahr.com/en/index.php?option=com_news&nid=1494&Itemid=2&task=displaynews#.Uzor__mSykE |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2月5日，据报道在莫克镇北部、索兰镇（Soran）和莫克镇南部的高速公路政府军与反对派武装发生交战。有报道显示索兰镇已经被政府军攻占。<ref name="soran">{{Cite web |url=http://syriahr.com/en/index.php?option=com_news&nid=1537&Itemid=2&task=displaynews#.UzqpYfmSykE |title=violent clashes continue in Hama |accessdate=2014-04-20 |archive-date=2014-04-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140421064442/http://syriahr.com/en/index.php?option=com_news&nid=1537&Itemid=2&task=displaynews#.UzqpYfmSykE |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2月11日，据报道莫克镇南部的al-Aboud检查站遭到自杀式汽车炸弹袭击，至少10名亲政府武装分子丧生。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://syriahr.com/en/index.php?option=com_news&nid=1633&Itemid=2&task=displaynews#.UzqqkfmSykE |title=More than 60 regular forces and NDF killed in the past 3 days |accessdate=2014-04-20 |archive-date=2014-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407095904/http://syriahr.com/en/index.php?option=com_news&nid=1633&Itemid=2&task=displaynews#.UzqqkfmSykE |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2月17日，据报道政府军对莫克镇发动猛攻，但被反对派武装击退。当天晚些时候政府军再次进入了莫克镇周边地区。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/72307 |title=Syria Rebels Seize Checkpoints in Aleppo, Deir Ezzor, Hama |accessdate=2014-04-20 |archive-date=2018-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180110234203/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/72307 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2月28日，根据当地活动人士报道，叙利亚政府军成功向莫克镇推进，推进过程中有激烈交火和猛烈轰炸发生。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://syriahr.com/en/index.php?option=com_news&nid=1805&Itemid=2&task=displaynews#.Uzqr2PmSykE |title=Violent clashes continue in Hama |accessdate=2014-04-20 |archive-date=2014-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407095514/http://syriahr.com/en/index.php?option=com_news&nid=1805&Itemid=2&task=displaynews#.Uzqr2PmSykE |dead-url=no }}</ref>

3月4日，在莫克镇南部的国际公路上有激烈冲突发生，而莫克镇西部地区遭到政府军空袭。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://syriahr.com/en/index.php?option=com_news&nid=1838&Itemid=2&task=displaynews#.UzqsjvmSykE |title=Violent clashes and raids in Hama and Hasakah provinces |accessdate=2014-04-20 |archive-date=2014-04-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140421064445/http://syriahr.com/en/index.php?option=com_news&nid=1838&Itemid=2&task=displaynews#.UzqsjvmSykE |dead-url=no }}</ref>

3月17日，莫克镇周边地区有激烈冲突发生。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContent/2/8/97477/World/Region/Syria-rebels-on-northern-offensive-after-losses.aspx |title=Syria rebels on northern offensive after losses |accessdate=2014-04-20 |archive-date=2017-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019085341/http://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContent/2/8/97477/World/Region/Syria-rebels-on-northern-offensive-after-losses.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>

3月24日，SOHR声称政府军试图突破反对派在莫克镇的防线，但数次尝试均被反对派武装击退。<ref>[http://syriahr.com/index.php?option=com_news&nid=17439&Itemid=2&task=displaynews#.Uz61t_mSykE استشهاد11 مقاتل من الكتائب الاسلامية باشتباكات مع القوات النظامية] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140828011814/http://www.syriahr.com/index.php?option=com_news&nid=17439&Itemid=2&task=displaynews |date=2014-08-28 }}</ref>

4月4日，据报道有6名反对派武装在莫克镇周边的冲突中丧生。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2014/Apr-14/253242-assad-says-war-has-reached-turning-point-in-favor-of-regime.ashx#axzz2ypbSb8JP |title=Assad says war has reached turning point in favor of regime |accessdate=2014-04-20 |archive-date=2017-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019184747/http://www.dailystar.com.lb//News/Middle-East/2014/Apr-14/253242-assad-says-war-has-reached-turning-point-in-favor-of-regime.ashx#axzz2ypbSb8JP |dead-url=no }}</ref>

4月14日，政府军占领了莫克镇部分地区。

10月23日，政府軍在親政府民兵的支援下完全收復莫克鎮。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2014/Oct-23/275130-army-retakes-key-syrian-town-from-rebels-monitor.ashx#axzz3GzPyK3Ra|title=Army retakes key Syrian town from rebels: monitor|work=The Daily Star Newspaper - Lebanon|accessdate=2014-10-25|archive-date=2017-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019185019/http://www.dailystar.com.lb//News/Middle-East/2014/Oct-23/275130-army-retakes-key-syrian-town-from-rebels-monitor.ashx#axzz3GzPyK3Ra|dead-url=no}}</ref>超過200名伊斯蘭陣線武裝分子、27名敘利亞陸軍士兵和32名國防軍民兵在最後一個星期的戰鬥中喪生。<ref name="itmeen">{{cite web|url=http://www.almasdarnews.com/article/hama-battle-map-update-syrian-army-captures-tal-itmeen|title=Hama Battle Map Update: Syrian Army Captures Tal Itmeen|publisher=Al-Masdar News|date=2014-10-23|accessdate=2014-10-24|archive-date=2017-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171009211015/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/hama-battle-map-update-syrian-army-captures-tal-itmeen/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

